<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ublogs..</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            /* To prevent horizontal scrolling */
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        nav h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            padding-right: 20px;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin-right: 20px;

        }

        nav ul li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            color: #ffcc00;
        }

        h1 {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 80px;
            /* Adjusted margin for space below fixed navbar */
            color: white;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .article-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            z-index: -1;
            border-radius: 8px;
            filter: blur(0.5px);
        }
        .article-container {
            color: white;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-width: 5px;
            border: 0.1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.482);
            box-shadow: 0 0px 0px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .article-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            object-fit: cover;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .article-container h2 {
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .article-container p {
            color: white;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            z-index: 10;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav>
        <h3>UBlogs..</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/blogs">blogs</a></li>
        </ul>
        <ul>
            {{#if user}}
            {{#if user.isAdmin}}
            <li><a href="/admin/blogs">{{user.username}}</a></li>
            {{else}}
            <li><a href="/dashboard">{{user.username}}</a></li>
            {{/if}}
            {{else}}
            <li><a href="/login">login</a></li>
            <li><a href="/register">register</a></li>
            {{/if}}
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <h1>Welcome to Ublogs..</h1>
    <div class="article-container" style="color: white;">
        <h2>Why Blogging is Important</h2>
        <p>Blogging has become an integral part of our digital age, providing individuals and businesses with a
            powerful
            platform to express ideas, share knowledge, and connect with a global audience. Here are some compelling
            reasons why blogging is important:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Express Yourself:</strong> Blogging allows you to express your thoughts, opinions, and
                creativity in a unique and personal way. Share your experiences, insights, and stories with the
                world.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Build an Online Presence:</strong> A blog serves as your online identity. It helps you
                establish
                credibility, showcase your expertise, and build a positive online reputation.</li>
            <li><strong>Connect with Others:</strong> Blogging enables you to connect with like-minded individuals,
                communities, and potential collaborators. It fosters meaningful conversations and relationships.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Share Knowledge:</strong> Whether you're an expert in a specific field or passionate about a
                particular subject, blogging allows you to share your knowledge and educate others. Contribute to
                the
                collective wisdom of the internet.</li>
            <li><strong>Boost SEO and Visibility:</strong> Regularly updating your blog with relevant content
                improves
                your website's search engine ranking. This increased visibility can lead to more opportunities and
                traffic.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Start your blogging journey today and experience the numerous benefits it brings to your personal and
            professional life!</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>